MOTU x TMNT: Turtles of Grayskull Action Figure Donatello 14 cm
products.description: Masters of the Universe. Approximate figure size: 14cm. Articulated figure. This Turtles of Grayskull action figure of Donatello from MOTU Origins depicts the exciting union of the Ninja Turtles and Masters of the Universe worlds as they clash in the Reptile Wars. The Ninja Turtles scour Eternia in search of Shredder, only to find themselves caught up in King Hiss' plot to turn the Snake Men into the most powerful force in the universe. This 14cm scale figure of Donnie de Grayskull has 16 movable joints for impressive battle poses and action moves from the Reptilian War. Donatello has a removable waist band, shoulder armour, hood and snake-patterned face shield. He is equipped with a staff with removable mace-like ends and removable flame effects. His turtle shell also serves as a frontal shield. The included mini-comic illustrates the story of the Reptile War, which can encourage creative play and expose the two worlds!

products.description: Masters of the Universe. Approximate figure size: 14cm. Articulated figure. This Rattler action figure from Turtles of Grayskull depicts the exciting fusion of the Ninja Turtles and Masters of the Universe worlds, as they clash in the Reptilian War. Mutated by green fluid, Rattler is a skull-headed reptiloid. The Ninja Turtles scour Eternia in search of Shredder, but find themselves caught up in King Hiss' plot to make the Snake Men the most powerful force in the universe. This 14.7cm skull-headed Grayskull Rattlor figure features a translucent body with 16 movable joints, including his distinctive tail and a long, fully articulated neck with ball joints, ending in a hinged jaw. The mutant Rattlor figure sports a snake-headed neck, bone harness and bone gauntlets, all of which are removable. For more storytelling fun than ever before, the figure even makes a rattling sound when shaken. The included mini-comic illustrates the story of the Reptile War, which can encourage creative play and expose the two worlds!
